window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>The first three action thrillers in the </b><b><i>USA Today</i></b><b> best-selling Mitch Herron series: </b><b><i>The Omega Strain</i></b><b>, </b><b><i>The Shadow Enclave</i></b><b>,</b><b><i> </i></b><b>and </b><b><i>The Lazarus Protocol</i></b><b>.&nbsp;</b></p> <p>Mitch Herron&nbsp;is a deadly assassin. No stakes are too high for his unique set of skills, until a routine mission goes horribly wrong. When Herron is forced down a deadly path to save millions of innocents, his only chance at redemption pits him against his shadowy employers.&nbsp;Can Herron prevail in a battle of killers?&nbsp;</p> <p>In a fight for control of the shadows, only one side can prevail. The explosive&nbsp;Mitch Herron series is&nbsp;perfect for fans of Lee Child, Mark Dawson, and David Archer.</p>"; 
